sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant GW as Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GenAI as gen-ai BFF<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser, ModelReg: Flow 1: User Dashboard Request (RHOAI 3.x)
    Browser->>GW: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>Session Cookie / OAuth
    GW->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS service-serving-cert<br/>Bearer Token
    KRBP->>KRBP: Validate: can user list<br/>project.openshift.io/projects?
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080 localhost)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
    Backend-->>Browser: React SPA (static assets)

    Note over Browser, ModelReg: Flow 2: K8s API Proxy (resource CRUD)
    Browser->>GW: POST /api/k8s/apis/... (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token
    GW->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>Bearer Token
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Proxy request (HTTPS/443)<br/>User's Bearer Token (impersonation)
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s API Response
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser, ModelReg: Flow 3: Module Federation (Gen AI BFF)
    Browser->>GW: POST /gen-ai/api/v1/responses (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token
    GW->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>GenAI: Proxy (HTTPS/8143)<br/>TLS shared proxy-tls cert<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    GenAI->>LlamaStack: LLM Inference (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token
    LlamaStack-->>GenAI: Inference Response
    GenAI-->>Backend: JSON Response
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser, ModelReg: Flow 4: WebSocket K8s Watch
    Browser->>GW: GET /wss/k8s/... (WSS/443)<br/>Upgrade: websocket
    GW->>KRBP: Forward (WSS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (WS/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: Watch (WSS/443)<br/>base64url.bearer.authorization<br/>subprotocol
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch Events (streaming)
    Backend-->>Browser: WebSocket Events

    Note over Browser, ModelReg: Flow 5: Prometheus Metrics Query
    Browser->>GW: POST /api/prometheus/query (HTTPS/443)
    GW->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Backend->>Thanos: PromQL Query (HTTPS/9092)<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    Thanos-->>Backend: Metrics Data
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser, ModelReg: Flow 6: Pipeline Execution
    Browser->>GW: POST /api/service/pipelines/... (HTTPS/443)
    GW->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)
    Backend->>DSP: Pipeline API (HTTPS/8443)<br/>ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    DSP-->>Backend: Pipeline Response
    Backend-->>Browser: JSON Response
